lead_paragraph: A confused referee sparked howls of protest on social media for sin-binning the wrong brother during the Cardiff Blues-Scarlets clash in rugby's Pro12 competition on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Referee Sin-Bins Wrong Brother in Welsh Match
